text: Wolf-Dieter Rihs (born 30 March 1950) is an Austrian equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1950 births Category:Living people Category:Austrian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Austria Category:Equestrians at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
